CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 19 reads: "9. Miss Marcella Palmer, hostess for the 1957 Plymouth line of cars, demonstrates why "suddenly it's 1960!"
TitMainTitle: Marcella Palmer standing beside Plymouth car filled with people, with banner reading "Suddenly it's 1960...Plymouth," at 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Syria Mosque
